<P>
 Thomas W. Velleca has been named to the new position of senior vice president 
of exploration of Arco.Velleca, 60, had been senior vice president of 
Exploration for Arco International Oil & Gas Co. Velleca will be based in 
Plano, Texas, and report directly to Executive Vice President William E. Wade 
Jr. in Los Angeles. Velleca will manage the various processes assuring the best 
allocation of exploration capital, prospect selection and the direction of 
exploration research. He will also be responsible for developing and placing 
exploration personnel. Velleca joined the Los Angeles-based oil company in 1993 
after a long career with Shell Oil Co. 
